quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  32,21,"Walanutheeqannahum mina alAAathabial-adna doona alAAathabi al-akbari laAAallahumyarjiAAoon"
  32,22,"Waman athlamu mimman thukkirabi-ayati rabbihi thumma aAArada AAanhainna mina almujrimeena muntaqimoon"
  32,23,"Walaqad atayna moosaalkitaba fala takun fee miryatin min liqa-ihiwajaAAalnahu hudan libanee isra-eel"
  32,24,"WajaAAalna minhum a-immatan yahdoonabi-amrina lamma sabaroo wakanoo bi-ayatinayooqinoon"
  32,25,"Inna rabbaka huwa yafsilu baynahumyawma alqiyamati feema kanoo feehiyakhtalifoon"
  32,26,"Awa lam yahdi lahum kam ahlakna minqablihim mina alqurooni yamshoona fee masakinihim inna feethalika laayatin afala yasmaAAoon"
  32,27,"Awa lam yaraw anna nasooqu almaaila al-ardi aljuruzi fanukhriju bihi zarAAanta-kulu minhu anAAamuhum waanfusuhum afala yubsiroon"
  32,28,"Wayaqooloona mata hatha alfathuin kuntum sadiqeen"
  32,29,"Qul yawma alfathi la yanfaAAuallatheena kafaroo eemanuhum wala hum yuntharoon"
  32,30,"FaaAArid AAanhum wantathirinnahum muntathiroon"
